<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>اشحن لعبتك المفضلة مجاناً</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    body {
      background: #0d0d0d;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #00ffcc;
    }
    .games-container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    .game-card {
      background: #1a1a1a;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px #00ffcc33;
    }
    .game-card img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .game-card h2 {
      margin: 10px 0;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .game-card a {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #00ffcc;
      color: #000;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>اختر لعبتك المفضلة واشحن مجاناً!</h1>

  <div class="games-container">

    <div class="game-card">
      <img src="https://i.imgur.com/VnQh9MF.jpg" alt="Roblox">
      <h2>شحن Robux مجاني</h2>
      <a href="locker.html">ابدأ الآن</a>
    </div>

    <div class="game-card">
      <img src="https://i.imgur.com/mVW4X8h.jpg" alt="Fortnite">
      <h2>شحن V-Bucks مجاني</h2>
      <a href="locker.html">ابدأ الآن</a>
    </div>

    <div class="game-card">
      <img src="https://i.imgur.com/v4G1ElB.jpg" alt="Free Fire">
      <h2>شحن Free Fire مجاناً</h2>
      <a href="locker.html">ابدأ الآن</a>
    </div>

    <div class="game-card">
      <img src="https://i.imgur.com/x5o1fh7.jpg" alt="PUBG">
      <h2>UC مجاني لـ PUBG</h2>
      <a href="locker.html">ابدأ الآن</a>
    </div>

    <div class="game-card">
      <img src="https://i.imgur.com/yLCWpWS.jpg" alt="Minecraft">
      <h2>احصل على Minecraft مجاناً</h2>
      <a href="locker.html">ابدأ الآن</a>
    </div>

    <div class="game-card">
      <img src="https://i.imgur.com/4xO4hO1.jpg" alt="GTA">
      <h2>هدايا داخل GTA 5</h2>
      <a href="locker.html">ابدأ الآن</a>
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>